OL,3,CPost Office campaigner says he will
OL,4,Creject 'offensive' compensation offer
OL,6,FThe former subpostmaster who has led
OL,7,Fthe campaign for justice in the Post
OL,8,FOffice Horizon scandal said he will
OL,9,Freject an offer of compensation from
OL,10,Fthe Government.
OL,12,FAlan Bates, whose two-decade fight
OL,13,Finspired the ITV series Mr Bates vs
OL,14,FThe Post Office, told The Daily
OL,15,FTelegraph the offer was "offensive"
OL,16,Fand "cruel".
OL,18,FThe Government confirmed plans for
OL,19,F"full and fair compensation" to
OL,20,Fsubpostmasters affected by the IT
OL,21,Fscandal in 2022.
