OL,3,CPost Office campaigner says he will
OL,4,Creject 'offensive' compensation offer
OL,6,FBut Mr Bates said the compensation
OL,7,Foffer had been "around a sixth" of
OL,8,Fwhat he requested.
OL,10,FHe told the Telegraph: "'Full and
OL,11,Ffair' might be His Majesty's
OL,12,FGovernment's interpretation, but in
OL,13,Freality the offer is derisory,
OL,14,Foffensive and after all this time,
OL,15,Fyes, cruel.
OL,17,F"I will absolutely be turning this
OL,18,Foffer for financial redress down.
