OL,3,CPost Office campaigner says he will
OL,4,Creject 'offensive' compensation offer
OL,6,F"It's just a terrible way to treat
OL,7,Fhuman beings ` and I have heard from
OL,8,Fseveral subpostmasters who have
OL,9,Freceived similarly derisory offers,
OL,10,Fwhile others are still waiting."
OL,12,FHe said the offer had been made on
OL,13,FWednesday, 111 days after his claim `
OL,14,Fprepared with the help of forensic
OL,15,Faccountants engaged by his lawyers `
OL,16,Fhad been submitted.
