OL,3,CPost Office campaigner says he will
OL,4,Creject 'offensive' compensation offer
OL,6,F"I have been in the queue along with
OL,7,Fall the others in the scheme, but if
OL,8,Fmy case is an example of the way they
OL,9,Fare going to treat all cases, we may
OL,10,Fas well start looking at a legal
OL,11,Faction again and let the judiciary
OL,12,Fdecide."
OL,14,FMr Bates was among more than 500
OL,15,Fpeople who received an average of
OL,16,Fabout #20,000 after a High Court
OL,17,Fruling in 2019.
